{"tid":1488483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[齊撐機場] 機場7月接待旅客數量較去年同期增長1%","createTime":"2019-08-19T15:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T15:46:17.000Z","uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc8c446f4073c8ea2746dc496c104e6f8b478ce","tid":1488483,"uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"2019-08-19 HKT 23:18<br />\n<br />\n機場管理局公布，香港國際機場 7 月的航空交通量，機場接待旅客 670 萬人次，較去年同月增長 1%。<br />\n<br />\n飛機起降量則較去年同期增加 0.4% 至 36845 架次，貨運量則減少 7.3% 至 401000 公噸。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">轉機或過境旅客量則較去年同期上升 11%</span></span>，帶動客運量增長，來往東南亞及日本的整體客運量錄得最明顯升幅。<br />\n<br />\n進口及轉口貨運量減少 12% ，以致該月貨運量下跌。在各主要貿易地區中，以來往東南亞及北美洲的貨運量跌幅最為顯著。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">被班藍絲攻擊時就分享數據啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2075980d14b174b92056f10e1c79c5254ee9bcc2","tid":1488483,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"[8.19] 係咪覺得今日好多帶風向POST？幫你一次過睇晒重點！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KwAJ47Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKwAJ47Q.png&h=ccc0ccf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488468</a>"},{"pid":"b668c6a55329048d4488c846cea357331c3f3f64","tid":1488483,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:46:17.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<